<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Delivered - QuickBite</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1f2937;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo img {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .checkmark {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 32px;
    }
    .rating-stars {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .star {
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #d1d5db;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .rating-form {
      background: #fefce8;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background: #22c55e;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 8px;
    }
    .button-outline {
      background: white;
      color: #22c55e;
      border: 2px solid #22c55e;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 24px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="QuickBite">
      </div>
      <div class="checkmark">🎉 ✅ 🍕</div>
      <h1>Order Delivered!</h1>
      <div>Order #{{orderId}}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>,</p>
      
      <p>Great news! Your order from <strong>{{restaurantName}}</strong> has been delivered successfully.</p>
      
      <div style="background: #f0fdf4; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <strong>📋 Order Summary</strong><br>
        Total Amount: ৳{{totalAmount}}<br>
        Delivery Address: {{deliveryAddress}}<br>
        {{#if agentName}}
          Delivered by: {{agentName}}<br>
          Agent Contact: {{agentPhone}}
        {{/if}}
      </div>
      
      <div class="rating-form">
        <h3>How was your experience?</h3>
        <p>Rate your order for <strong>{{restaurantName}}</strong></p>
        
        <div class="rating-stars">
          <a href="{{reviewUrl}}?rating=5" class="star">★</a>
          <a href="{{reviewUrl}}?rating=4" class="star">★</a>
          <a href="{{reviewUrl}}?rating=3" class="star">★</a>
          <a href="{{reviewUrl}}?rating=2" class="star">★</a>
          <a href="{{reviewUrl}}?rating=1" class="star">★</a>
        </div>
        
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">Click on a star to leave a rating and review</p>
      </div>
      
      <center>
        <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" class="button">📝 Leave a Review</a>
        <a href="{{orderAgainUrl}}" class="button button-outline">🔄 Order Again</a>
      </center>
      
      <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 20px;">
        Loved your experience? Share your feedback and help us improve!
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>QuickBite • Delivering happiness to your doorstep</p>
      <p>Follow us for exclusive offers 🎉</p>
      <p>© {{year}} QuickBite. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>